SELECT ?first ?last ?workTel
WHERE
{
  ?person ab:firstName ?first ;
          ab:lastName ?last .
  OPTIONAL
  { ?person ab:workTel ?workTel . }
}

1)to optional einai join,alla ean den exo timi to afino keno
  (anti na petaxo tin grami)

  px 2150 takis kariadis

     mpori na bro to 2150 ston optional ara tha tou balo 1 nil

2)episis to optional perni ta var-domains tou pano pinaka
  san arxikes times ton dikon tis var-domains